Attribute.value: OSINT investigation based on the original tweet from Liu Ya which contains a netfilter/iptables script with some IP addresses. By pivoting from the IP addresses, malware samples and script can be found at different locations. This quick analysis include the scripts collected, the samples and the relationships between the various objects.
